data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News Chain data analyst Yu Jin Monitoring said that the creator of Broccoli (contract 0x6d5...714) token on BNBChain used Broccoli to turn 1 BNB (about $707) into 9,819 BNB (about $6.72 million) in 24 minutes, earning 9,517 times the profit. Now these profitable BNBs have been sold by him in exchange for ETH+USDT+USDC.
The specific operations of the creator are as follows: 
1. After CZ posted a tweet about his dog Broccoli, Broccoli was quickly created on four.meme (contract 0x6d5...714); 
2. Immediately after creation, 1 BNB (about 707 US dollars) was used to purchase 115.4 million Broccoli, with an average price of 0.000006123 US dollars; 
3. Subsequently, user funds poured in after seeing CZ's tweet, quickly pushing Broccoli's market value to 400 million US dollars; 
4. In 24 minutes, these 115 million tokens were sold to retail investors who were FOMO in 12 transactions in exchange for 9,819 BNB (about 6.72 million US dollars); 
5. Finally, the BNB was transferred to the 0xc77...894 address and all sold in exchange for 200 ETH+3.357 million USDT+2.62 million.
